  "name": "Endless Paladin",
  "title": "Champion of the Black Flames",
  "description": "The servants of Orcanix know no death. Should they be reduced to dust, their master will summon them to her Pyre and create their bodies anew. Even so, nothing can be destroyed again and again without consequence.\n\nThe Paladins have no flesh, no blood. Some have lost even their bones, existing more as ghostly wraiths than moving corpses. They would wear their twisted husks with pride, if they could feel such things. But rebirth demands a price far beyond the physical, and they have paid in full.\n\nNothing remains inside them but bloodlust and blind obedience.",
